1acda35c-7fd0-49b1-b836-ce6903bd09e0.title: Counter Strike 1.6
1acda35c-7fd0-49b1-b836-ce6903bd09e0.summary: Counter-Strike (also known as Half-Life: Counter-Strike or Counter-Strike 1.6) is a 2000 tactical first-person shooter game developed by Valve Corporation and published by Sierra Studios. It is the first installment in the Counter-Strike series.
